trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class encapsulates the transport security settings for queued transports.
trans-unit.target: La classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> encapsule les paramètres de sécurité de transport pour les transports de mise en file d'attente.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialise une nouvelle instance de la classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class, using an existing instance.
trans-unit.target: Initialise une nouvelle instance de la classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> à partir d'une instance existante.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Obtient ou définit le <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> associé à cette instance de la classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> associé à cette instance de la classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: MSMQ can authenticate messages that are sent to message queues that require authentication, or messages can explicitly request authentication.
trans-unit.target: MSMQ peut authentifier les messages envoyés aux files d'attente de messages qui requièrent une authentification ou les messages peuvent demander explicitement une authentification.

trans-unit.source: The default authentication mode is <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode.WindowsDomain>.
trans-unit.target: Le mode d'authentification par défaut est <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode.WindowsDomain>.

trans-unit.source: The value is not one of <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> values.
trans-unit.target: La valeur ne fait pas partie des valeurs <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Obtient ou définit le <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> associé à cette instance de la classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> associé à cette instance de la classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: MSMQ can encrypt messages on the wire when transferring messages between message queue managers.
trans-unit.target: MSMQ peut chiffrer des messages sur le câble lors du transfert de messages entre des gestionnaires de files d'attente de messages.

trans-unit.source: The default encryption algorithm is <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm.RC4Stream>.
trans-unit.target: L'algorithme de chiffrement par défaut est <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm.RC4Stream>.

trans-unit.source: The value is not one of <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> values.
trans-unit.target: La valeur ne fait pas partie des valeurs <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Obtient ou définit le <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> associé à cette instance de la classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: The default protection level is <xref:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel.Sign>.
trans-unit.target: Le niveau de protection par défaut est <xref:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel.Sign>.

trans-unit.source: The value is not one of the <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> values.
trans-unit.target: La valeur ne fait pas partie des valeurs <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" />.

trans-unit.source: The default hash algorithm is <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm.Sha1>.
